283
00:28:52,397 --> 00:28:54,524
Round and round she goes.

284
00:28:54,599 --> 00:28:57,397
No more bets.
Where she stops, nobody knows.

285
00:28:57,469 --> 00:29:01,337
Good luck. And the number is...

286
00:29:04,275 --> 00:29:07,676
