298
00:29:41,146 --> 00:29:44,047
- And I mean no limit.
- Twenty dollars.

299
00:29:45,483 --> 00:29:47,383
Yeah.
No, no, I think...

300
00:29:47,452 --> 00:29:50,615
I'm making a joke here.
Just give me a thousand.

