00:29:50,688 --> 00:29:53,248
Give me a thousand bucks.
Tab it.

302
00:29:54,959 --> 00:29:58,326
Would you like a table for the late
show, Jackie Shore, Constellation Room?

303
00:29:58,396 --> 00:30:00,887
- In the back.
- One thousand dollars.

304
00:30:02,333 --> 00:30:04,130
- Thanks.
