305
00:30:04,202 --> 00:30:05,669
Excuse me.

306
00:30:07,172 --> 00:30:10,471
If you got the name,
go get the game.

307
00:30:10,542 --> 00:30:12,442
Let's gamble.

308
00:30:12,510 --> 00:30:13,909
Okay.

309
00:30:13,978 --> 00:30:15,912
No, hey, this is for show.

310
00:30:15,980 --> 00:30:17,914
Play what you got
